  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">LIP-READING AND FACIAL EXPRESSION are very critical to deaf and hard of hearing 4 effective communication.  We will produce face mask for deaf with the clear space that will enable deaf and hard of hearing to express themselves effectively through facial expression and lip-reading hence mitigating communication barrier that has existed. The organisation will assign trained deaf tailors to sew and produce face mask for deaf and distribute them free to hearing impaired and hard of hearing persons.</narrative>
  </description>
